---
title: Chicken Schnitzel & Zingy Apple Slaw Panini with Potato Wedges & Garlic Aioli
description: This chicken schnitzel sando is our crunchiest creation yet. Golden crumbed schnitzel and a crisp, refreshing slaw come together in
the middle of a perfectly toasted panini for the ultimate handheld meal. That first crunch will be heard throughout the house!
